Source: pg-fsql
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/yurc/pg_fsql

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-fsql
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-fsql
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Recursive SQL template engine for PostgreSQL
  pg_fsql provides a recursive SQL template engine implemented with C and
  PL/pgSQL, packaged here for PostgreSQL 14 through 18.
